>>SOURCE FORMAT FREE
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. MAIN.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 OUTER_P0 PIC 9.
01 OUTER_RES PIC 9.
01 PLUSONE_P0 PIC 9.
01 PLUSONE_RES PIC 9.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    COMPUTE OUTER_P0 = 3
    PERFORM FOUTER
    DISPLAY OUTER_RES
    STOP RUN.
.
FPLUSONE.
    COMPUTE PLUSONE_RES = PLUSONE_P0 + 1
    EXIT.
FOUTER.
        COMPUTE PLUSONE_P0 = OUTER_P0
        PERFORM FPLUSONE
    COMPUTE OUTER_RES = PLUSONE_RES
    EXIT.
